<p><strong>Agent Seymour:</strong> President Obama, I'm glad to speak to you. I have a very important message.</p>
<p><strong>Barack Obama:</strong> Who is this?</p>
<p><strong>Agent Seymour:</strong> Cliff Donald Sir, working for the Federal Bureau of Investigation. Just so I know this is the right person, I need you to quickly scratch your nose.</p>
