<div class="blockquote">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>Containment Log 5092-1-A</strong></p>
</div>
<br />
<strong>Goal:</strong> To make President Barack Obama initiate nose scratching before 21:00.
<p><strong>Personnel involved</strong>: TMTF Epsilon-33, comprised of Agents Young-Soo Ryu (Commander), Rose Maryland, Henry Farmer, Jarvis Bradley, Sam McCarthy, Sara Lineham, and Benjamin Jackson.</p>
<p><strong>Containment Plan:</strong> Agents Ryu, Maryland, Farmer, and Bradley (ε-33-A) would enter the White House under the guise of Secret Service and locate the President while Agents McCarthy, Lineham, and Jackson (ε-33-B) secure the perimeter under the guise of cleaners and gardeners.</p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>[Begin Log, 20:26]</strong></p>
</div>
<p><em>Note: For clarity, non-Foundation persons have been highlighted in blue.</em></p>
<p><em>AT 20:26 TMTF ε-33 leaves Site-10&#160;en route to The White House in a black van (driven by Agent Farmer) disguised as a Secret Service vehicle.</em></p>
<p><strong>Site-12 Command:</strong> Thirty-four minutes to midnight.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Young-Soo Ryu:</strong> We're ten minutes away from the target.</p>
<p><strong>Command:</strong> Copy.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Henry Farmer:</strong> Wait, ten minutes? I'm not sure we can get there in less than fiftee-</p>
<p><strong>Agent Ryu:</strong> Ten minutes.</p>
<p><em>There is the sound of screeching tires as ε-33 speeds up, swerving around multiple vehicles.</em></p>
<p><strong>Agent Farmer:</strong> Shit!</p>
<p><em>Multiple car horns can be heard behind ε-33.</em></p>
<p><strong>Command:</strong> Is everything alright?</p>
<p><strong>Agent Ryu:</strong> Everything is going fine comman- RUN THAT RED LIGHT!</p>
<p><em>ε-33 turns, barely avoiding collision with a blue car. Multiple screams are heard behind ε-33.</em></p>
<p><strong>Agent Farmer:</strong> <em>FUCK!</em></p>
<p><strong>Command:</strong> Ryu, we've just been informed MTF Alpha-45 (&quot;Janitors&quot;) are on their way to assist with any post-mission cleanup.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Rose Maryland:</strong> Wait, why are <em>we</em> looking for the President? Isn't that place full of cameras?</p>
<p><strong>Agent Ryu:</strong> Yes, but they aren't live. They just store their recordings and send them to Site-10 each hour. They're old too. Half of them don't even- Turn right there! -work right.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Maryland:</strong> What cheap losers would-?</p>
<p><em>Agent Maryland is cut off as the contents of the vehicle, including herself, lurch to the side.</em></p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>[Cut to 20:35]</strong></p>
</div>
<p><strong>Agent Ryu:</strong> We've arrived at the target location.</p>
<p><strong>Command:</strong> Copy.</p>
<p><em>ε-33's vehicle abruptly stops in front of the White House.</em></p>
<p><strong>Agent Ryu:</strong> (<em>To Agents McCarthy, Lineham, and Jackson</em>) Wait three minutes before getting out of the vehicle. Make sure no one sees you exit.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Sam McCarthy:</strong> Understood.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Maryland:</strong> Shit. eight o'clock.</p>
<p><em>50 meters away two men in dark suits are watching the vehicle.</em></p>
<p><strong>Agent Ryu:</strong> Ignore them. Follow me.</p>
<p><em>Agent Ryu steps out of the vehicle and heads towards the White House entrance, followed by Agents Maryland, Farmer, and Bradley. All are disguised as Secret Service.</em></p>
<p><strong>Command:</strong> Twenty-three minutes to midnight.</p>
<p><em>ε-33-A enters the White House entrance. Ten seconds later they are stopped by a man in a grey suit.</em></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #0d0690">Unidentified Man</span>:</strong> Do you mind if I see your ID?</p>
<p><em>Agent Maryland shows the man an ID card. The man inspects it for five seconds, then nods.</em></p>
<p><em>Agent Ryu heads to the area surrounding the West Wing, Agent Maryland the East Wing, Agent Farmer the basement and Agent Bradley the Residence Villa.</em></p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>[Cut to 20:42]</strong></p>
</div>
<p><strong>Command:</strong> Eighteen minutes to midnight.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Ryu:</strong> Any sign of the President yet?</p>
<p><strong>Agent Jarvis Bradley:</strong> Negative.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Maryland:</strong> Same here.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Farmer:</strong> (<em>whispering</em>) Nothing in the basement so far.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Ryu:</strong> The Oval Office was empty. I'm heading to the Vice President's now.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Farmer:</strong> Wait, wh- what if the President isn't in the White-</p>
<p><em>While Agent Farmer speaks, Agent Ryu slowly opens the door to the Vice-President's office.</em></p>



<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment:scp-5092-2/MoreObama"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/fragment:scp-5092-2/MoreObama/medium.jpg" style="width:300px;" class="enlarge" alt="MoreObama" /></a>
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>Stillframe from Agent Ryu's bodycam footage. (20:43)</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong><span style="color: #0d0690">Vice-President Joe Biden</span>:</strong> Hey Barack, take a look at this funny dog video my grandson sent me!</p>
<p><em>Joe Biden and Barack Obama begin watching the video.</em></p>
<p><strong>Agent Ryu:</strong> I've located the President. Get to the Vice-President's office now.</p>
<p><em>Joe Biden and Barack Obama finish watching the video after seven seconds.</em></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #0d0690">President Barack Obama</span>:</strong> (<em>Laughs</em>) That's great Joe!</p>
<p><strong>Agent Ryu:</strong> Excuse me, Mr. President.</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #0d0690">Obama</span>:</strong> Huh?</p>
<p><em>President Obama notices Agent Ryu and looks up to face him.</em></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #0d0690">Joe Biden</span>:</strong> What's this?</p>
<p><strong>Agent Ryu:</strong> Mr. President, I need you to do me a favor.</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #0d0690">Obama</span>:</strong> What? Who are you?</p>
<p><strong>Agent Ryu:</strong> Listen, Sir, I don't have much time to explain, you've been infected with an experimental new mind weapon. You nee-</p>
<hr />
<p><strong>Agent Bradley:</strong> (<em>Speaking to a man in a grey suit</em>) I'm quite sure you have the wrong person, I'm- Hey! stop that-</p>
<hr />
<p><em>Agent Bradley's line cuts out.</em></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #0d0690">Obama</span>:</strong> Infected? Infected by who?</p>
<p><strong>Agent Ryu:</strong> Russian-</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #0d0690">Biden</span>:</strong> This is crazy! The hell are you on about?</p>
<p><strong>Command:</strong> Fifteen minutes to midnight.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Ryu:</strong> Look I just need you to-</p>
<p><em>Three gunshots are heard in the hallway outside the Vice-President's office.</em></p>
<p><strong>Agent Ryu:</strong> <em>Shit!</em> Obama, just scratch-</p>
<p><em>Agent Ryu steps towards Obama.</em></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #0d0690">Biden</span>:</strong> If you take one step closer bud, I'll mess you up. Even more than- than- what was his name? Oh! Cornpop! Yea, watch out buddy!</p>
<p><em>Agent Jackson enters the room, flinging open the door. There is blood on his lower torso.</em></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #0d0690">Biden</span>:</strong> This is malarkey! Hold on Barack, let me just call-</p>
<p><strong>Agent Jackson:</strong> For the love of-</p>
<p><em>Agent Jackson grabs and pushes Joe Biden against the wall, then injects him with a dose of Class B amnestics. While Joe Biden begins to slowly fall unconscious, Agent Jackson exits the room and re-enters dragging an unconscious man in a grey suit behind him. The lower portion of the man's suit is stained with blood.</em></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #0d0690">Biden</span>:</strong> Gonna.. Gonna stop you man&#8230;</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #0d0690">Obama</span>:</strong> Oh my god! What do you want?!</p>



<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment:scp-5092-2/ObamaAgain"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/fragment:scp-5092-2/ObamaAgain/medium.jpg" style="width:300px;" class="enlarge" alt="ObamaAgain" /></a>
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>Stillframe from Agent Ryu's bodycam footage. (20:46)</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>Agent Ryu:</strong> I need you to scratch your nose!</p>
<p><em>Obama is silent for a moment.</em></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #0d0690">Obama</span>:</strong> Scratch my-</p>
<p><em>Obama pauses, looking at Agent Ryu with a confused facial expression.</em></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #0d0690">Obama</span>:</strong> Wait.. a minute. Did you call me while-</p>
<p><em>Agent Ryu draws his gun.</em></p>
<p><strong>Agent Ryu:</strong> Scratch your fucking nose, Obama!</p>
<p><em>Obama scratches his nose.</em></p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>[End Log]</strong></p>
</div>
<p><strong>Aftermath:</strong> At 21:07, MTF Alpha-45 (&quot;Janitors&quot;) arrived at the White House to perform post-mission cleanup. Amnestics were given to all non-Foundation personnel involved, the White House was restored to its previous state, and any unknown civilian witnesses outside the White House were later discredited.</p>
