<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>Containment Log 5092-1-B</strong></p>
</div>
<p><strong>Goal:</strong> To make President Barack Obama initiate nose scratching before 21:05.</p>
<p><strong>Personnel involved:</strong> Agent Rose Lineheart of MTF Theta-20 (&quot;Sniffle Squad&quot;), embedded in the White House Secret Service following Incident 5092-1-A.</p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>[Begin Log, 20:02]</strong></p>
</div>
<p><strong>Site-143 Command:</strong> Agent Lineheart, we have been informed that 5092-1 has materialized. Current intel suggests that President Obama is located in the White House. The rest of Theta-20 will arrive in five minutes.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Rose Lineheart:</strong> Where's the President at?</p>
<p><strong>Site Command:</strong> Cameras are showing President Obama is in the Resident Villa.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Lineheart:</strong> Copy, heading to Resident Villa.</p>
<p><em>Agent Lineheart reaches the Resident Villa after five minutes, occasionally diverting paths to avoid suspision.</em></p>
<p><strong>Agent Lineheart:</strong> I have reached the target's location. Is there anyone else in the Villa?</p>
<p><strong>Site Command:</strong> Not currently. Target appears to be asleep. The use of T-128C is suggested.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Lineheart:</strong> Copy, proceeding to target.</p>
<p><em>Agent Lineheart spends three minutes silently walking towards the target's bedroom.</em></p>
<p><strong>Agent Lineheart:</strong> I have reached the target's location. Entering now.</p>
<p><em>Agent Lineheart slowly pushes open the door to the Obama's bedroom. He is sleeping in his bed. Agent Lineheart slowly walks towards his location and examines him.</em></p>
<p><em>Agent Lineheart removes T-128C from her suit and removes the cap.</em></p>
<p><strong>Agent Lineheart:</strong> (<em>whispering</em>) Deploying T-128C now.</p>
<p><strong>Site Command:</strong> Copy.</p>
<p><em>Agent Lineheart deploys T-128C on Obama. After seven seconds there is no physical response.</em></p>
<p><strong>Agent Lineheart:</strong> <em>(whispering)</em> No response from target. Attempting again.</p>
<p><strong>Site Command:</strong> Understood. Caution is advised.</p>
<p><em>Agent Lineheart deploys T-128C on Obama for a second time, this time on a different location on the nose. After five seconds, there is still no response from Obama.</em></p>
<p><strong>Agent Lineheart:</strong> (<em>whispering</em>) No response, preparing for third deployment.</p>
<p><strong>Site Command:</strong> Granted, proceed.</p>
<p><em>As Agent Lineheart is about to use T-128C again, Obama rolls over in bed. Agent Lineheart pauses briefly, checking the status of the target. Obama appears to still be asleep. Agent Lineheart waits one minute before continuing.</em></p>
<p><strong>Agent Lineheart:</strong> Initiating.</p>
<p><em>Lineheart deploys T-128C on Obama's nose. After five seconds, Obama moves his arm to his face and tickles the underside of his nose.</em><br /></p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>[End Log]</strong></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
