<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="blockquote">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>Containment Tool 128C</strong></p>
</div>
<p><strong>Designed For:</strong> MTF Theta-20, for the purpose of neutralizing SCP-5092-1 in case the President is sleeping during an SCP-5092-B event.</p>
<p><strong>Designed By:</strong> Dr. Everret Kris, senior engineer at Site-88's Safe-Object Containment Wing.</p>
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:400;"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment:scp-5092-2/Tool"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/fragment:scp-5092-2/Tool/medium.jpg" style="width:400;" alt="Tool" class="image" /></a>
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:400;">
<p>The final prototype of T-128C, held by Dr. Kris.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>Use Guide:</strong> T-128C is a metal and rubber cylinder with a flashlight at the top and a thin slit on the base. At the back of the cylinder, there is a switch that is used to turn the flashlight off and on.</p>
<p>A discreet button at the bottom of the cylinder is used to eject a feather-like apparatus from the slit. The same button can be used to retract the feather back into the slit. A plastic cap can be placed over the base to hide the slit. To remove the cap, squeeze both sides and twist.</p>
<p>The feather-like device can be used to create 'ticklish' or 'itchy' feelings in conscious or unconscious individuals in order to elicit a physical response (rubbing the affected area).</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><em>Note: Two months after Incident 5092-1-B, a newly engineered meme, designed to make its host scratch their nose at 19:53, was transmitted to President Obama. No more 5092-B events occurred for the remainder of Obama's presidency, possibly as a result of the meme.</em></p>
</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>Incident 5092-1-C, 2020/5/29</strong></p>
</div>
<div class="blockquote">
<p>At 20:54, The COEWS detected that SCP-5092-1 had manifested 59&#160;400km away from Earth and would collide in 55m at 20:49. At 19:55, Overseer Command declared a code black emergency and enacted Protocol 34. (Protocol 27 could not be enacted due to the lack of notice to the object's arrival).</p>
<p>At 19:57, a Theta-20 Agent contacted President Donald Trump and attempted to coax him into scratching his nose.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">⮝&nbsp;Show&nbsp;Call&nbsp;Transcript</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">⮟&nbsp;Close&nbsp;Call&nbsp;Transcript</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="blockquote">
<p><em>The following is the transcript of a call between Agent Claudia Archer and President Donald Trump</em></p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>[Begin Log, 29:57]</strong></p>
</div>
<p><strong>Donald Trump:</strong> Hello?</p>
<p><strong>Agent Archer:</strong> Hello Mr President, it's fantastic to talk to you. I'm from the Federal Bureau of Investigation.</p>
<p><strong>Donald Trump:</strong> Well, thank you very much! You know, I hear there are many fine people- brilliant people- at the FBI.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Archer:</strong> Thank you Mr. President. I have a very important message for you.</p>
<p><strong>Donald Trump:</strong> Is this about those anarchists and looters? Right now, they are destroying this fantastic city. If you were here, well you might be but you understand, I guarantee you would be very upset. Everyone here is you know. But many people are scared to say it. But I'm being told, that there isn't anything else we can do. And you see people say, &quot;oh, we can't be brutal. The police are being too brutal. We have to save the poor people&quot; But what about our beautiful churches? What about St Johns? They set it on fire, you know. Very horrible.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Archer:</strong> Yes. Yes, definitely. As I was saying, I have a message from Director Wray.</p>
<p><strong>Donald Trump:</strong> You know, I sometimes get the sense that Director Wray doesn't like me very much. But I do admire him. Very strong man.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Archer:</strong> Agreed. So Director Wray wanted to let you know- (<em>Agent Archer pauses</em>) Sorry, I just had a bit of nose itch.</p>
<p><strong>Donald Trump:</strong> It's funny. I seem to get a lot of those.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Archer:</strong> Oh, really? I experience the same thing!</p>
<p><strong>Donald Trump:</strong> Oh yes. I'll be doing important work- which, you know, many people say I don't do work, and it's just not true, I do a lot more work than many other people, very important work, then I see people saying &quot;Oh, that man doesn't do work&quot;. But yes, I will be at my desk, and I will often get scratches. And it doesn't seem to leave. You know, sometimes you have an itch, like a toe itch, and it might be there for a while- and will be very annoying- but it will go away. And it is very strange if it doesn't go away. And I often think &quot;this itch will go away&quot;, and then a few days later I have another nose itch. And I told- well I don't remember who it was exactly- but they said &quot;Donald, you should talk to a doctor&quot; and I just think, what a waste of time it would to see a doctor because my nose is itchy. Maybe it isn't. But I think it is.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Archer:</strong> Maybe you should see a doctor? You never know with these things. Maybe it's a symptom of a bigger problem that you don't know about?</p>
<p><strong>Donald Trump:</strong> Yes, I did think, maybe it is a problem. But I don't think it is. I'm very healthy. I often get people- maybe doctors- telling me &quot;You are very healthy for your age. I haven't met people at your age that healthy&quot; and it would just be very strange- not impossible- but strange if I had, perhaps, one of those, nose cancers, or other very bad diseases.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Archer:</strong> (<em>To Operator Atkins</em>) Has 5092-1 dematerialized?</p>
<p><strong>Operator Atkins:</strong> Not yet.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Archer:</strong> Well you know, even very healthy people get health problems. They say that noses are, uh, very vulnerable areas.</p>
<p><strong>Donald Trump:</strong> Many people say that &quot;Oh, healthy people get just as many diseases as large people&quot;. but I don't think it is true- maybe in some cases- many healthy people are getting the ChinaVirus, which is very, very unfortunate- but that's how diseases work, it's very difficult to avoid. Many people say to wear the facemasks, but we just aren't sure how much they help. You know, Fauci was saying first, &quot;Oh, don't wear the mask. They are ineffective&quot;, and now he's saying &quot;Wear the mask, everyone needs to wear the masks&quot; and, you know, he might be right, he's a very, very smart man. But we just aren't sure how important they are right now.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Archer:</strong> (<em>To Operator Atkins</em>) Anything?</p>
<p><strong>Operator Atkins:</strong> No sir.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Archer:</strong> (<em>To Operator Atkins</em>) This isn't working.</p>
<p><strong>Agent Archer:</strong> Well sir, it has been a pleasure speaking to you. It seems we may even have something in common in the nose department! Director Wray just wanted to let you know that he will have a very important report on your desk tomorrow.</p>
<p><strong>Donald Trump:</strong> Goodbye. Very good talk!<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>[End Log]</strong></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">⮟&nbsp;Close&nbsp;Call&nbsp;Transcript</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>At 20:48, Theta-20 successfully neutralized the threat.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">⮝&nbsp;Show&nbsp;Containment&nbsp;Log</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">⮟&nbsp;Close&nbsp;Containment&nbsp;Log</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="blockquote">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>Containment Log 5092-1-C</strong></p>
</div>
<p><strong>Goal:</strong> To make President Donald Trump initiate nose scratching before 20:45. 20:49 at the latest.</p>
<p><strong>Personnel involved:</strong> MTF Theta-20 (&quot;Sniffle Squad&quot;), transported in two vehicles.</p>
<p><strong>Containment Plan:</strong> Theta-20 would break into the Presidential Emergency Operations Center and make President Trump scratch his nose.</p>
<p><strong>Prior Events:</strong> Theta-20 Agents embedded within the White House Secret Service attempted to reach the President, however, the President had been moved to the underground Presidential Emergency Operations Center (due to safety concerns regarding the protests occurring around Capitol Hill at the time), and the Theta-20 Agents were not given access. Backup was required to forcefully bypass high security.</p>
<p><strong>Event log:</strong></p>
<table class="wiki-content-table">
<tr>
<th>Time</th>
<th>Event</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>19:48</td>
<td>As they drive, Theta-20 vehicles begin dispensing large amounts of tear gas ahead of them to disperse the protestors crowding the streets. Multiple times, protestors attempted to assault the vehicles and had to be shot with rubber bullets to allow Theta-20 to keep moving.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>20:12</td>
<td>Theta-20's vehicles stop outside of Lafayette Square.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-7" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-7')">7</a></sup> Theta-20 exit the vehicles and approach the police line.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>20:15</td>
<td>The Theta-20 Commander shows the officers at the front of the police line their valid Secret Service credentials. The police officer expresses surprise, and decides to radio his superiors to ask about Theta-20.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>20:16</td>
<td>His superior expresses confusion at Theta-20's arrival, and after 50 seconds it is clear that Theta-20 is not going to be given immediate access.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>20:17</td>
<td>Theta-20 decides to forcefully bypass the police line. The two vehicles, parked roughly 10 meters away from the police line, begin to dispense aerosolized amnestic/sedative gas in the surrounding area, subduing and amnesticizing protestors, while Theta-20 rush the police line and attack the police officers with electroshock batons.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>20:18</td>
<td>As the White House security begins preparation for an imminent attack from Theta-20, agents embedded within the White House begin jamming all communications to and from the White House.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>20:21</td>
<td>As Theta-20 reaches the halfway point across Lafayette Square, hidden White House snipers begin firing upon the Task Force. Multiple agents are hit, mostly due to the lack of cover in the Park.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>20:25</td>
<td>Cameras show a dozen well-armed Government Agents waiting for Theta-20 in the Diplomatic Reception Room and surrounding area. To ambush them, Theta-20 first deployed a silencing turtle (SCP-███), to surround the White House with a field of sound wave suppression, then detonated remote explosives on the back wall to gain entry.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>20:26</td>
<td>Theta-20 attack the WH agents from behind, engaging in a firefight that causes considerable damage to the White House interior and results in multiple Theta-20 casualties. White House goes on full lockdown.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>20:32</td>
<td>Theta-20 uses remote explosives to break through a secure blast door leading into the East Wing. Embedded Agents disable traps.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>20:33</td>
<td>A Remote Concentrated Energy Turret located in the East Wing hallway terminates four Theta-20 Agents before being neutralized via grenade.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>20:35</td>
<td>Theta-20 is jumped by five heavily armored officers armed with shotguns. Upon termination, the final officer self-detonates, killing multiple Theta-20 Agents.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>20:41</td>
<td>Theta-20 Agents use remote demolition to break through a reinforced steel door.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>20:43</td>
<td>After fighting a few more White House agents, Theta-20 again use remote demolition to break into the underground Presidential Emergency Operations Center.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>20:44</td>
<td>Theta-20 enter the Operations Center and terminate several hostile agents. Since they cannot speak due to the ongoing effects of the silencing turtle, Theta-20 attempt to communicate to Donald Trump with sign language that he needs to scratch his nose.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>20:48</td>
<td>After four minutes of trying various forms of communication without success, a Theta-20 agent grabs onto Trump's arm and physically forces him to scratch his own nose.</td>
</tr>
</table>



<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:208px;"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment:scp-5092-2/trump"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/fragment:scp-5092-2/trump/medium.jpg" style="width:208px;" class="enlarge" alt="trump" /></a>
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:208px;">
<p>Stillframe from Agent Foxtrot's bodycam footage. (20:48)</p>
</div>
</div>



<div class="scp-image-block block-left" style="width:208px;"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment:scp-5092-2/troops"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/fragment:scp-5092-2/troops/medium.jpg" style="width:208px;" class="enlarge" alt="troops" /></a>
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:208px;">
<p>Stillframe from Agent Delta's bodycam footage. (20:14)</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>Aftermath:</strong> At 20:49, MTF Alpha-45 (&quot;Janitors&quot;) arrived at the White House to perform post-mission cleanup. The White House was repaired, all witnesses were amnesticized (largely through the mass use of aerosolized amnestic gas deployed under the guise of tear gas), witnesses unaccounted for were discredited, and dead US government personnel were erased from all records.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">⮟&nbsp;Close&nbsp;Containment&nbsp;Log</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>At 20:49, The COEWS detected that SCP-5092-1 had dematerialized. At 20:51, Overseer Command declared the end of the code black emergency and Protocol 34.</p>
</div>
<hr />
